Author: ifuckpineapples
Text: for what it's worth, I recently got my blood work done as part of my physical and my doctor said everything looked good. but when I brought a copy to my Ed specialist, she compared it to "blood work warning signs of anorexia" doc she had and I was in the low or danger range for everything...despite being in the safe range according to the basic blood test. even if you seem healthy to a usual doctor, a specialist can know what to look for
